snippet.title: Settler Gameplay - Comicon Africa Release
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay video for the Comicon Africa/Project Springbok release version of Settler.
If you like what you see please download and rate our game! It will help us out a lot!
Game Page: https://project-springbok.itch.io/settler-cca-version
